{{% example csharp %}}
```csharp
using System.IO;
using Pulumi;
using Aws = Pulumi.Aws;

class MyStack : Stack
{
    public MyStack()
    {
        var example = new Aws.CloudFront.PublicKey("example", new Aws.CloudFront.PublicKeyArgs
        {
            Comment = "test public key",
            EncodedKey = File.ReadAllText("public_key.pem"),
        });
    }

}
```
